Description: django-debug-toolbar-requests
        =============================
        Adds requests debuging information
        
        Setup
        -----
        Add the following lines to your ``settings.py``::
        
           INSTALLED_APPS = (
               ...
               'requests_toolbar',
               ...
           )
        
           DEBUG_TOOLBAR_PANELS = (
               ...
               'requests_toolbar.panels.RequestsDebugPanel',
               ...
           )
